@page "/minecraft-server-rules"

<PageTitle>Minecraft Server Rules - SentrySMP</PageTitle>

<p>
    By playing on our server, you agree with <b>all</b> these rules:
</p>
<h3>👥 #1: Respect Other Players</h3>
<p>
    Keep the chat friendly and respectful. No harassment, hate
    speech, or excessive toxicity.
</p>

<h3>🏰 #2: Griefing and Raiding are Allowed</h3>
<p>
    Griefing and raiding bases are part of the gameplay—protect your
    stuff (Spawn Griefing is not allowed and gets you a perm IP ban.
    )!
</p>

<h3>🚫 #3: No Cheating or Exploits</h3>
<p>
    Hacked clients, X-ray mods, and exploiting bugs are strictly
    prohibited.
</p>

<h3>⚡ #4: No Lag Machines</h3>
<p>
    Don't create anything that causes excessive lag for the server.
</p>

<h3>💬 #5: Chat Conduct</h3>
<p>
    Avoid spamming, advertising, or sharing inappropriate content in
    chat.
</p>

<h3>⚔️ #6: PvP is Enabled</h3>
<p>
    PvP is allowed, but no intentional harassment or targeting of
    specific players.
</p>

<h3>⚖️ #7: Staff Decisions Are Final</h3>
<p>Listen to staff members and follow their instructions.</p>

<p>Effective Date: November 21, 2025</p>